-			 * the dedicated BPID recorded by xsk_pool_attach().
-			 * Until sub-increment 2 reprograms the FMan RX port's
-			 * primary BPID, fd->bpid stays the kernel page BPID and
-			 * this stays 0 -- proving the recognition path is sound
-			 * with zero datapath risk. Spec sec 6.1.7 / 6.1.10.
-			 */
-			if (fd->bpid == priv->xsk_bpid[_band]) {
-				priv->xsk_zc_eligible++;
-				/* M3-3 step 7 sub-increment 3 (patch 0096): true-ZC RX
